The LightDM Webkit Greeter
==========================

The lightdm-webkit-greeter is a greeter that can be themed using html and
javascript via webkit.

Two example greeters are supplied: webkit, and simple.  The webkit greeter
is more graphical, while the simple theme implements a minimalistic login
screen.

For documentation, see the supplied manpage.

The project is hosted on Launchpad.  You can find it at:

https://launchpad.net/lightdm-webkit-greeter
